<template>
	<search :iconType="iconType"></search>
</template>

<script>
	import search from "../search.vue";
	export default {
		components:{
			search
		},
		data() {
			return {
				title: 'Hello',
				iconType:['success', 'success_no_circle', 'info', 'warn', 'waiting', 'cancel', 'download', 'search', 'clear']
			}
		},
		onLoad() {
			// #ifdef APP-PLUS|| MP-WEIXIN
			this.iconType = ['success', 'success_no_circle', 'info', 'warn', 'waiting', 'cancel', 'download', 'search', 'clear']
			// #endif
			// #ifdef MP-ALIPAY
			this.iconType = ['info', 'warn', 'waiting', 'cancel', 'download', 'search', 'clear', 'success', 'success_no_circle',
				'loading'
			]
			// #endif
			// #ifdef MP-BAIDU
			this.iconType = ['success', 'info', 'warn', 'waiting', 'success_no_circle', 'clear', 'search', 'personal', 'setting',
				'top', 'close', 'cancel', 'download', 'checkboxSelected', 'radioSelected', 'radioUnselect'
			]
			// #endif
		},
		methods: {

		}
	}
</script>

<style>
	.content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.logo {
		height: 200rpx;
		width: 200rpx;
		margin-top: 200rpx;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		margin-bottom: 50rpx;
	}

	.text-area {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.title {
		font-size: 36rpx;
		color: #8f8f94;
	}
</style>
